strings: <voice_0x01000BFF><se_low>King of tricks: Hi Media! At my house! It's the same thing!
<voice_0x01000C00><se_low>King of tricks: I miss you It's okay! Either way, get out of this horrible place now.
<voice_0x01000C01><se_low>King of tricks: My daughter followed suit. Be careful not to over bend it.
<voice_0x01000C04><se_def>China: In order to get rid of them, you have to work hard. However, we apologize for the inconvenience.
<voice_0x01000C05><se_def>China: Farewell, the angels will protect you.
